<!--
  Per-seed text overrides for Archipelago.

  Mod ships with this empty placeholder. The sibling AP-companion app
  rewrites this file in the installed mod directory after scouting the
  AP server, before the player clicks Start Game. Civ 7 reads it via
  the <UpdateText> action declared in archipelago.modinfo at
  new-game-start, applying the per-seed display overrides to the
  game's database. Tree-cards then render AP item names natively.

  Hand-editing this file in the source tree has no effect at play
  time; the installed copy is what Civ 7 loads.
-->
